---
title: Golden Fried Chicken Wings and Ranch Wedge Salad with Sweet Potato Dippers
description: When it comes to chicken wings, there is no two ways about it: They are at their crispiest when fried to golden perfection! We'll walk you through every step of how to prepare and cook this  beloved finger food, which pairs perfectly with a refreshing, crisp wedge salad.
